Content.summary: 'Pho Map' - a blog post by Darren Ferguson about United Kingdom, food ratings, Hospitality Recreation written on 14 October 2006
Content.tags: United Kingdom, food ratings, Hospitality Recreation
Content.bodyText:
The Pho Map is a great resource if you are ever in the UK and are looking for a delicious bowl of Vietnamese noodle soup.

The map features clickable photos, and food ratings, and is growing weekly.
